    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Various types of events are organised every and a special guest such as a bollywood actor comes as a special guest for that event and you can get very skillful apportunities",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "In terms of students life the crowd is really awesome so many friendly students you can find here .and the girls and boys ratio is 70:30 respectively",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The professors are amazing they teach so well it's really easy to understand and worth to attend all the lectures  .",
          "name": "Sauleha shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library section is so huge and many books and novels are available and also all the subject books are available at no cost we can take study and return really amazing facility .",
          "name": "Sauleha shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College fest that taught me a lot from finances to marketing to how to handle meetings",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Decent faculty that encouraged in lot of extra curricular work.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers and Staff is friendly and understanding",
          "name": "Amruta Gawai",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Beautiful Scenery and It is right opposite to Girgaon Chowpatty",
          "name": "Amruta Gawai",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Great food in the canteen and great classrooms for students college also conducts social activities for the students to learn new things around earth",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Has events and fest so that students can enjoy and can have time for themselves out of stress of studies",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I really didn't liked a department which I would not like to mention here. Like they cannot understand students.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The crowd is a lottt during the fest times and it's really annoying that time because of rush it really seems irritating.",
          "name": "Sauleha shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college doesn't provide some facility like transport of bus taxis aren't available easy there.",
          "name": "Sauleha shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college doesn't have big campus area as compared to other colleges",
          "name": "Sauleha shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "the website that college uses is totally outdated or atleast during our time it was out dated.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Too many formal procedures to get the office work done should be an easy process.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Tech and Infra could have been better. I blame it to the University with outdated syllabus.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.M.M"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cafeteria is always filled with people but maybe thats a plus point as well",
          "name": "Amruta Gawai",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen walls needs to be developed also canteen should be kept clean as much as possible",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some teachers being rude to students without any reasons",
          "name": "Rating Sage",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ]
    },
